    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n        Jaki powinien być wyraz zaznaczony na czerwono, aby dzielenie można było wykonać bez reszty?\n    "
    },
    {
      "type": "spoiler",
      "label": "rozwiąż 6 przykładów",
      "body": "\n\n<div class=\"switch_steps\">\n<div class=\"switch_step\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 50px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                        1.\n                    </span>\n                    W działaniu \\((8x^2\\color{red}{-4x}):(4x-3)\\) czerwony wyraz powinien być równy\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(6x\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-6x\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-3x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<p>\n                    Zgadza się:\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                (8x^2\\color{red}{-6x}):(4x-3)=\\frac{8x^2-6x}{4x-3}=\\frac{2x(4x-3)}{4x-3}=2x\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 50px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                        2.\n                    </span>\n                    W działaniu \\((6x^3+\\color{red}{10x^2}):(2x+5)\\) czerwony wyraz powinien być równy\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(15x^2\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-10x^2\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(15x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<p>\n                    Zgadza się:\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                (6x^3+\\color{red}{15x^2}):(2x+5)=\\frac{6x^3+15x^2}{2x+5}=\\frac{3x^2(2x+5)}{2x+5}=3x^2\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 50px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                        3.\n                    </span>\n                    W działaniu \\((-6x^3+\\color{red}{2x^2}):(3x-2)\\) czerwony wyraz powinien być równy\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-4x^2\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(4x^2\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(8x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<p>\n                    Zgadza się:\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                (-6x^3+\\color{red}{4x^2}):(3x-2)=\\frac{-6x^3+4x^2}{3x-2}=\\frac{-2x^2(3x-2)}{3x-2}=-2x^2\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 50px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                        4.\n                    </span>\n                    W działaniu \\((2x^3\\color{red}{-9x^2}):(2x-3)\\) czerwony wyraz powinien być równy\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-3x^2\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(3x^2\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(6x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<p>\n                    Zgadza się:\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                (2x^3\\color{red}{-3x^2}):(2x-3)=\\frac{2x^3-3x^2}{2x-3}=\\frac{x^2(2x-3)}{2x+5}=x^2\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 50px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                        5.\n                    </span>\n                    W działaniu \\((-6x^2+\\color{red}{13x}):(2x-3)\\) czerwony wyraz powinien być równy\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-9x\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(9x\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(3x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<p>\n                    Zgadza się:\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                (-6x^2+\\color{red}{9x}):(2x-3)=\\frac{-6x^2+9x}{2x-3}=\\frac{-3x(2x-3)}{2x-3}=-3x\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n<span style=\"display: inline-block; width: 50px; font-weight: bold;\">\n                        6.\n                    </span>\n                    W działaniu \\((4x+\\color{red}{1}):(2x-3)\\) czerwony wyraz powinien być równy\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-6\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(6\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-6x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<p>\n                    Zgadza się:\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                (4x\\color{red}{-6}):(2x-3)=\\frac{4x-6}{2x-3}=\\frac{2(2x-3)}{2x-3}=2\n                \\]\n                Możemy przejść do ostatniej metody dzielenia wielomianów.\n            </div>\n</div>\n"
    },
